  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ModelValueProvider
    Interface for model value providers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ASMMOMAModelValueProvider
    Computes the target value for individuals as in the ASM-MOMA [1] algorithm.
    FitnessModelValueProvider
    Provides the fitness of the individual from the archive as the fitness value.
    IdentityNormalizer
    Dummy normalizer which does not do any normalization.
    Linear01Normalizer
    Normalizes the inputs linearly to the 0-1 range.
    LogarithmicNormalizer
    Performs a logarithmic transformation of the input values.
    ModelInputNormalizer
    Interface for input normalizers.
    SearchItemIndividualArchive
    Implementation of the archive of SearchItemIndividuals.
    SurrogateFitnessFunction
    Fitness function which uses a model to predict the value instead of evaluating it directly.
    SurrogateMutationOperator
    Informed mutation based on the information from a surrogate model (Gaussian process regression).
